import React from 'react' import "../allcourses/courses.css" import { coursesCard } from "../../dummydata" import Title from '../common/title/Title' import { useTranslation } from 'react-i18next' const HAbout = () => { const [t, i18n] = useTranslation("global"); return ( <>
<div className='coursesCard'> {/* copy code form coursesCard */} <div className='grid2'> {coursesCard.slice(0, 3).map((val) => ( <div className='items'> <div className='content flex'> <div className='left'> <div className='img'> <img src={val.cover} alt='' /> </div> </div> <div className='text'> <h1>{t(`Habout.${val.serviceName}`)}</h1> <div className='rate'> <i className='fa fa-star'></i> <i className='fa fa-star'></i> <i className='fa fa-star'></i> <i className='fa fa-star'></i> <i className='fa fa-star'></i> <label htmlFor=''>(5.0)</label> </div> <div className='details'> {val.courTeacher.map((details) => ( <> <div className='para'> <h4>{details.name}</h4> </div> <span>{details.totalTime}</span> </> ))} </div> </div> </div> <div className='price'> <h3> {val.priceAll} / {val.pricePer} </h3> </div> <button className='outline-btn'>GET QUOTE!</button> </div> ))} </div> </div> </div> </section> </> ) } export default HAbout
